column2:
"That was incredible!
<%me>!
I was glued to the monitor!"

"Oh, right, I already said that. But I really
meant it, so don't be surprised if I keep
repeating myself!"

"I totally dug how you handled that! You
really know how to get the job done!"

"Now I feel like I could do it, too!
I mean, why should you get all the
attention all the time?"
